fast.Name: fast
fast.Description: moving or able to move, operate, function, or take effect quickly; quick; swift; rapid.

flying.Name: flying
flying.Description: making flight or passing through the air; that flies.

impenetrable.Name: impenetrable
impenetrable.Description: not penetrable; that cannot be penetrated, pierced, entered, etc.

invisible.Name: invisible
invisible.Description: not visible; not perceptible by the eye.

necromancer.Name: necromancer
necromancer.Description: a person who uses witchcraft or sorcery, especially to reanimate dead people or to foretell the future by communicating with them.

omniscient.Name: omniscient
omniscient.Description: having complete or unlimited knowledge, awareness, or understanding; perceiving all things.

protection_IV.Name: Protection IV
protection_IV.Description: The highest level of the Protection enchantment in Minecraft. Protection IV absorbs 16% of damage per armor piece.

skeletal.Name: skeletal
skeletal.Description: of, relating to, or like a skeleton.

Spider-.Name: Spider-
Spider-.Description: Characterizes someone as having powers identical to, or similar to, the American Superhero Spider-Man.

strong.Name: strong
strong.Description: having, showing, or able to exert great bodily or muscular power; physically vigorous or robust.

Super-.Name: Super-
Super-.Description: Characterizes someone as having powers identical to, or similar to, the American superhero Superman.

undead.Name: undead
undead.Description: no longer alive but animated by a supernatural force, as a vampire or zombie.

vampire.Name: vampire
vampire.Description: a preternatural being, commonly believed to be a reanimated corpse, that is said to suck the blood of sleeping persons at night.

wild_wild_west.Name: Wild Wild West
wild_wild_west.Description: Denotes someone as being of the wild wild west.
